利用requrst,使用首先要 使用方法</p>\n","bodyMarkdown":"","bodyHtml":"","rawMarkdown":"","plainText":"","toc":[],"slugForSearch":"cee10602","comments":true,"math":false,"mermaid":false},{"kind":"post","sourcePath":"source/_posts/snap删除旧的core-snap删除其他版本的软件.md","route":"/posts/b6b8953/","abbrlink":"b6b8953","title":"snap删除旧的core(snap删除其他版本的软件)","date":"2018-06-28 13:43:41","updated":"2018-06-28 13:43:41","tags":["Linux","Snap"],"categories":["Linux"],"language":"zh-Hans","htmlLang":"zh-Hans","locale":"zh_CN","textDirection":"ltr","dateLocale":"zh-CN","excerptMarkdown":"","excerptHtml":"<p>偶尔发现snap会自动升级core且不删除旧版，在’/snap/core’ 会发现好几个版本的文件夹。 使用 删除某个版本的core，xxx是软件的rev，使用 可以查看软件的rev，其他软件也能用这个方法删除旧的版本哦。 参考：How to unmount and possibly delete old Ubuntu Core snap</p>\n","bodyMarkdown":"","bodyHtml":"","rawMarkdown":"","plainText":"","toc":[],"slugForSearch":"b6b8953","comments":true,"math":false,"mermaid":false},{"kind":"post","sourcePath":"source/_posts/ubuntu终端下连接wifi.md","route":"/posts/fb6d8628/","abbrlink":"fb6d8628","title":"ubuntu终端下连接wifi","date":"2018-06-23 12:24:10","updated":"2018-06-23 12:24:10","tags":["Linux"],"categories":["Linux"],"language":"zh-Hans","htmlLang":"zh-Hans","locale":"zh_CN","textDirection":"ltr","dateLocale":"zh-CN","excerptMarkdown":"","excerptHtml":"<h2 id=\"首先使用rfkill查看你的wifi设备是否被停用\">首先使用rfkill查看你的wifi设备是否被停用</h2>\n<p>使用命令</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki code-block language-bash\"><code><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#B392F0\">rfkill</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\"> list</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>获得设备列表，每个都包含与之关联的索引号，从 0 开始<br>\n查看设备是否被停用，要启用被停用的设备，请运行：</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki code-block language-bash\"><code><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#B392F0\">rfkill</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\"> unblock</span><span style=\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F97583\"> &#x3C;</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\">索引</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">号</span><span style=\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F97583\">></span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>要启用所有设备，请运行：</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki code-block language-bash\"><code><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#B392F0\">rfkill</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\"> unblock</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\"> all</span></span></span></code></pre>\n","moreAnchor":"more","bodyMarkdown":"","bodyHtml":"","rawMarkdown":"","plainText":"","toc":[],"slugForSearch":"fb6d8628","comments":true,"math":false,"mermaid":false}]}